    "steam_appid": 3213540,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just Eat The Rich</strong> 是一款充满动作的基于波次的第一人称射击生存游戏，带有 roguelike 元素。你有 20 分钟的时间杀死富人，收集钱财并将他们的财富重新分配给穷人。 (简体中文): 独自玩或与朋友一起玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与 Boss 战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败最令人讨厌的亿万富翁，在你的十字军征程中与独特的 Boss 战斗，并在最不可思议的对决中将这些傲慢的富豪跪倒！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁武器和技能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级并从多种技能中选择，构建出最优化的财富分配方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用金钱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新投资你获得的资金，找到购买更强武器的地方，用你收集到的钱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集强力武器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有其他方式获得最强大的武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Birdman 不再等待</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >政客们失败了，现在是时候将问题（和金钱）掌握在自己手中了。装备好，闯入精英们的豪宅，开始 Just Eat the Rich</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>功能</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演 Birdman </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买武器 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择技能 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密升级组合 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新分配财富 </p></li></ul>",
